{"id":2357,"date":"2024-02-09T16:38:03","date_gmt":"2024-02-09T09:38:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/?p=2357"},"modified":"2024-03-27T13:38:26","modified_gmt":"2024-03-27T06:38:26","slug":"ca-sy-quach-tuan-du-hanh-trinh-cap-treo-nui-sam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/ca-sy-quach-tuan-du-hanh-trinh-cap-treo-nui-sam\/","title":{"rendered":"Ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i c\u00e1p treo vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>\u00a0Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u00e2n, ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i c\u00e1p treo vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean b\u00e1o An Giang: \u201cV\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng An Giang, vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, \u0111i c\u00e1p treo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 b\u1ec7 b\u00e0 ng\u1ef1 n\u0103m x\u01b0a, v\u1eeba ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, nhanh ch\u00f3ng, v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00e2m linh v\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u1ea3nh quan h\u00f9ng v\u0129, lung linh t\u1eeb tr\u00ean cao\u201d.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, d\u1ecbp T\u1ebft Nguy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1n 2024, ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du &#8211; \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Khu Du l\u1ecbch V\u0103n h\u00f3a t\u00e2m linh B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 &#8211; C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam c\u00f2n g\u1eedi t\u1eb7ng tr\u00ean 5.000 v\u00e9 m\u1eddi c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n c\u00e1c khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 b\u00e0 con h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Th\u1ecb x\u00e3 T\u00e2n Ch\u00e2u v\u00e0 t\u1ec9nh \u0110\u1ed3ng Th\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c qua T\u1ebft s\u1ebd \u0111i h\u1ebft c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb mi\u1ec1n trung, mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, mi\u1ec1n \u0110\u00f4ng Nam B\u1ed9 v\u00e0 TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chia s\u1ebb ni\u1ec1m vui b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng h\u00e1t ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t v\u00e9 m\u1eddi c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n c\u00e1c khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 b\u00e0 con h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u00e8o trong n\u0103m 2024.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image001_qtd.jpg\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image001_qtd-1024x1000.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2358\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 n\u00fai Sam b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1p treo<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image003_qtd.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"854\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image003_qtd-1024x854.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2359\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du cho bi\u1ebft, \u0111i c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n, v\u1eeba nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb tr\u00ean cao to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh n\u00fai Sam<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du chia s\u1ebb, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi con c\u1ee7a qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng An Giang, \u0111i l\u00e0m xa qu\u00ea, m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp T\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn, Xu\u00e2n v\u1ec1, vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua l\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam c\u1ea7u cho n\u0103m m\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, b\u00ecnh an, thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, c\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh danh to\u1ea1i. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam vi\u1ebfng b\u1ec7 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9. T\u1eeb khi c\u00f3 c\u00e1p treo, vi\u1ec7c l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u1eeb khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u1ed5ng C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ebfn ga \u0111i, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m tham quan, check-in c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p. Khi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eam b\u00e1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc &#8220;song sinh&#8221; v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u1ed9c v\u00eda B\u00e0, ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn quang c\u1ea3nh thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean\u2026, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f2n l\u01b0u luy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u00e2n t\u00e2m th\u01b0 th\u00e1i, an l\u1ea1c, tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y hy v\u1ecdng cho m\u1ed9t n\u0103m m\u1edbi sau chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image005_qtd.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"624\" height=\"351\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image005_qtd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2360\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image005_qtd.jpg 624w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image005_qtd-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image005_qtd-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng cao t\u1ed1c TP. HCM \u0111i An Giang nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb tr\u00ean cao<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00fang c\u1ed5ng khu du l\u1ecbch, du kh\u00e1ch nh\u1edb ch\u1ea1y th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o b\u00e3i \u0111\u1eadu xe c\u00f3 b\u1ea3ng d\u1eebng ch\u1eef P, \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n ch\u1ebfch v\u1edbi c\u1ed5ng ch\u00f9a B\u00e0. Ngay ph\u00eda tay ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a c\u1ed5ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ea7y b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u00e1p treo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image007_qtd.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image007_qtd-1024x1000.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2361\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image007_qtd-1024x1000.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image007_qtd-200x195.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image007_qtd-600x585.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image009_qtd.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image009_qtd-1024x1000.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2362\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u xe \u0111i\u1ec7n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, ch\u1edf du kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb c\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o t\u1edbi nh\u00e0 ga l\u00ean c\u00e1p treo, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1edf kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 ga \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e3i \u0111\u1eadu xe sau khi \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh chuy\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u1edfng ngo\u1ea1n t\u1eeb m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t l\u00ean t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh thi\u00eang c\u1ee7a n\u00fai Sam.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 T\u1ebft Nguy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1n Gi\u00e1p Th\u00ecn 2024, C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam ra m\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i gi\u00e1 m\u1edbi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00e1n b\u1ed9, c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi lao \u0111\u1ed9ng (xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh th\u1ebb c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn n\u01a1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c) v\u00e0 b\u00e0 con h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng (xe 16 ch\u1ed7 tr\u1edf l\u00ean), v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 c\u00e1p treo l\u00e0 79.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 9\/2 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft 9\/3\/2024.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u00a0M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp \u0111i An Giang qu\u00ea Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du, \u0111\u1ebfn TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i gh\u00e9 tham quan C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam, l\u00ean n\u00fai \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 b\u1ec7 B\u00e0. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i 24\/24h, hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 79.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng cho c\u00e1n b\u1ed9, c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi lao \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 du kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng theo tour xe t\u1eeb 16 ch\u1ed7 tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u2013 ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kinh t\u1ebf kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u00e3i nghi\u1ec7m\u201d.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"624\" height=\"624\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image011.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2363\" style=\"width:624px;height:auto\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image011.jpg 624w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image011-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image011-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image011-200x200.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image011-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image011-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image013.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image013.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2364\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image013.jpg 960w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image013-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image013-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image013-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image013-200x200.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image013-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image013-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp quanh n\u0103m<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image015.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image015.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2365\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image015.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image015-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image015-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Khu Du l\u1ecbch V\u0103n h\u00f3a t\u00e2m linh B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 &#8211; C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba, \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam, r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho du kh\u00e1ch.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 ga d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n n\u00fai \u2013 \u0111i\u1ec3m xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u00e1p treo, c\u00f3 nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh b\u1ed1n m\u00f9a, c\u1ea3nh s\u1eafc ba mi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0o d\u1ecbp T\u1ebft, C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1ea9n tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec3u c\u1ea3nh trang tr\u00ed T\u1ebft, \u0111i\u1ec3m check-in \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1ea1 v\u00e0 hoa ki\u1ec3ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 s\u1eafc m\u00e0u \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00f4 cho T\u1ebft Gi\u00e1p Th\u00ecn 2024 th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n l\u1ed9ng l\u1eaby \u0111\u1ec3 du kh\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1edfng ngo\u1ea1n, ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image017.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image017.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2366\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image017.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image017-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image017-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image019.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image019.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2367\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image019.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image019-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image019-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image021-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image021-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2368\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image021-1.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image021-1-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image021-1-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 n\u00fai Sam b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1p treo<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam n\u1eb1m trong qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 Khu Du l\u1ecbch V\u0103n h\u00f3a t\u00e2m linh B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9: Kh\u00f3m V\u0129nh T\u00e2y 3, ph\u01b0\u1eddng N\u00fai Sam, TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ec9nh An Giang.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean 10ha, b\u00e3i gi\u1eef xe c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a h\u01a1n 2.000 \u00f4t\u00f4. V\u1edbi b\u1ed1n s\u1ea3nh nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t\u2026, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, li\u00ean hoan, team building\u2026<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image023.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"624\" height=\"833\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image023.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2369\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image023.jpg 624w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image023-200x267.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image023-600x801.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>Khu Du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam g\u1ed3m h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e1p treo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 b\u1edfi C\u00f4ng ty MGA Vi\u1ec7t Nam, do c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 C\u1ed9ng h\u00f2a \u00c1o x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e1p c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i 900m, v\u1edbi 37 cabin. M\u1ed7i cabin ch\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u0111a 8 kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 di chuy\u1ec3n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00ean n\u00fai Sam vi\u1ebfng b\u1ec7 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image025.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"540\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image025.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2370\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image025.jpg 540w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image025-200x133.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image027.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"624\" height=\"462\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image027.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2371\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image027.jpg 624w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image027-200x148.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image027-600x444.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>B\u1ec7 B\u00e0 \u2013 N\u01a1i c\u00f3 t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng truy\u1ec1n B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam t\u1eebng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00edn c\u00f4 g\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed3ng trinh th\u1ec9nh xu\u1ed1ng ch\u00e2n n\u00fai<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image029.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"825\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image029-1024x825.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2372\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>T\u1eeb tr\u00ean c\u00e1p treo ng\u1eafm to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam, chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt Th\u00edch Ca ng\u1ed3i thi\u1ec1n, cao 81m, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt Th\u00edch Ca t\u1ea1c v\u00e0o n\u00fai cao to nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi c\u00f4ng, theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u0103m 2025<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ec9nh thi\u00eang n\u00fai Sam, l\u00e0m l\u1ec5 t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7 B\u00e0, tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i b\u1ed9 xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00e0 ga c\u00e1p treo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng, du kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed thi\u00eang li\u00eang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ec1n, ch\u00f9a, \u0111i\u1ec7n, \u0111\u00e0i v\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac c\u1ed5 x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. Quanh kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 h\u1ed3 c\u00e1 Koi, thung l\u0169ng t\u00ecnh y\u00eau\u2026 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i, nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u t\u00ecnh duy\u00ean linh \u1ee9ng\u2026.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa x\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam, S\u01a1n l\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, ch\u00f9a T\u00e2y An, ch\u00f9a Hang, du kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam c\u00f2n c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp chi\u00eam b\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em &#8220;song sinh&#8221; v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u201cPh\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc H\u00f2a b\u00ecnh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc d\u00f9ng ch\u1ebf t\u00e1c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c ng\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i v\u00f9ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc Vancouver (Canada) n\u1eb7ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn h\u01a1n 10 t\u1ea5n, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cm\u1ecf qu\u00fd\u201d c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1ec1 tr\u1eef l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi nguy\u00ean kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t qu\u00fd hi\u1ebfm kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang t\u1ea1i v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00e0y m\u00e0 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1edbi nguy\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc H\u00f2a b\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1eafp s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ebfn to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&#8221;, \u00a0b\u1edfi nh\u00e0 ti\u00ean tri Zopa Rinpoche ti\u00ean \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng Ian Green, th\u00ec t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc n\u00fai Sam mang s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh \u201can l\u00e0nh v\u00e0 b\u00ecnh an cho nh\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i\u201d.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image031.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"684\" height=\"971\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image031.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2373\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image031.jpg 684w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image031-200x284.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image031-600x852.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 684px) 100vw, 684px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc H\u00f2a b\u00ecnh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image032.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"854\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image032-1024x854.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2374\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image034.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"854\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image034-1024x854.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2375\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image036.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"810\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image036-1024x810.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2376\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image038.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image038-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2377\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image038-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image038-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image038-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image038-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image038-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image038-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image040.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"854\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image040-1024x854.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2378\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>C\u1ea7u t\u00ecnh y\u00eau tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image042.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"967\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image042-1024x967.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2379\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image044.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"854\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image044-1024x854.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2380\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du ng\u1eafm to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c b\u1eb1ng \u1ed1ng nh\u00f2m tr\u00ean C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image046.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image046.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2381\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image046.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image046-200x133.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image046-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110i c\u00e1p treo, du kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u01b0\u1ee1i m\u00e2y, r\u1ebd gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. Nh\u00e0 ga c\u00e1p treo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu Nh\u00e0 th\u1edd \u0110\u1ee9c B\u00e0, t\u1ea1i TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 ga l\u00e0 m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac &#8220;ch\u00f9a M\u1ed9t C\u1ed9t&#8221;, v\u1edbi h\u1ed3 sen ph\u00eda d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u1edf quanh n\u0103m. Ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa \u201cch\u00f9a M\u1ed9t C\u1ed9t\u201d v\u00e0 c\u1eeda nh\u00e0 ga c\u00e1p treo, l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t theo ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 du kh\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e3m v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0: B\u00edch h\u1ecda, 36 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, ru\u1ed9ng l\u00faa tr\u0129u h\u1ea1t, nh\u00e0 tre m\u00e1i l\u00e1 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y s\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec7m may mi\u1ec7t v\u01b0\u1eddn gi\u1ea3n d\u1ecb, \u0111\u01a1n s\u01a1\u2026.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image048.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image048.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2382\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image048.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image048-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image048-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image050.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image050-1024x1000.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2383\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du tham quan Nh\u00e0 may C\u00f4 3 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ea1i C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image052.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"854\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image052-1024x854.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2384\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image054.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image054.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2385\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image054.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image054-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image054-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image056.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image056.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2386\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image056.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image056-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image056-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, du kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u0103n h\u00f3a mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o khi quan s\u00e1t nh\u1eefng show l\u00f4t\u00f4 di\u1ec5n ra li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y. Ng\u1eafm TP.Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam, trong c\u00e1i se l\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n vi\u1ec5n bi\u00ean, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image058.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image058.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2387\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image058.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image058-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image058-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image060.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"684\" height=\"513\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image060.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2388\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image060.jpg 684w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image060-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image060-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 684px) 100vw, 684px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image062.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"607\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/image062-1024x607.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2389\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed xe \u0111i\u1ec7n, mi\u1ec5n v\u00e9 tr\u1ebb em d\u01b0\u1edbi 1,2m v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cao tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean 70 tu\u1ed5i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Khu Du l\u1ecbch V\u0103n h\u00f3a t\u00e2m linh B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 &#8211; C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam, mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o, kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u0103n ho\u00e1 t\u00e2m linh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh tham quan, c\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e2n h\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n: B\u00e1o An Giang<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00a0Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u00e2n, ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i c\u00e1p treo vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean b\u00e1o An Giang: \u201cV\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng An Giang, vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, \u0111i c\u00e1p treo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 b\u1ec7 b\u00e0 ng\u1ef1 n\u0103m x\u01b0a, v\u1eeba ti\u1ec7n [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[79],"tag